{"tid":446540,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"(求救) 隻狗冇事呀可","createTime":"2017-10-24T11:36:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-24T18:10:49.000Z","uid":131293,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"6d660523abd8cf564cfbbe4c4023cf0143f991a9","tid":446540,"uid":131293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T11:36:08.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n我起身食緊朱古力可可脆加奶嗰啲唔小心倒瀉咗幾粒朱古力可可脆落地下<br />\n我嗰時都唔為意<br />\n食食吓 突然隻狗衝咗過嚟食咗<span style=\"color: red;\">幾粒</span><br />\n應該冇事呀可<br />\n隻狗唔係我 係host family<br />\n聽講狗唔食得朱古力<br />\n而家仲跳下跑下<br />\n我怕佢過多陣消化緊嗰時仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人可以話比我聽點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我知我錯了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://holland.pk/nfy1x539\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fnfy1x539&h=df4890bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ed4fb8d5295b2e488adee46364bab04517381475","tid":446540,"uid":131293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T11:36:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"43b9cf6327b399ef8910b01440a13953d72893a7","tid":446540,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T11:37:12.000Z","msg":"會嘔到成地都係"},{"pid":"ca100f77f41140244c31bbed20dec3fc90d9046a","tid":446540,"uid":131293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T11:37:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/t356mhan\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ft356mhan&h=6fb0bb04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n狗仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbe1fc830dcd0e16016af749852f61b754701460","tid":446540,"uid":131293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T11:38:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會嘔到成地都係</blockquote><br />\n唔好嚇我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96b4148a7f4f6f8e4bcfac98